      "description": "The US Treasury 2 Year Note ETF (UTWO) is an exchange-traded fund that is based on the Bloomberg US Treasury Bellwether 2Y index. The fund is a passively managed, single-bond fund that invests in the most recently issued, on-the-run, 2-year US Treasury note. The fund is designed for those specifically required to track the 2-year tenor on the yield curve. UTWO was launched on Aug 9, 2022 and is issued by F/m Investments.",
